Body: Description: The scan ran for several days, now showing an error message. Tried to close the running.lck file (6604) but couldn't find it in task manager. Rebooted the server, same issue. I'll attach a screenshot.

What We've Learned Updated: 1) kill the process (if you can find it) in Task Manager > Details (or Processes) TAB
2) AND delete the "running.lck" 
3) AND reboot the server (if needed).
